{"tid":1249444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邊個先係真新聞...?","createTime":"2019-06-21T17:18:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T09:21:22.000Z","uid":107860,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5aefedc4effe8112b19f3e87dcb992b57c6c3b76","tid":1249444,"uid":107860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:18:24.000Z","msg":"咁岩睇完兩個post...但係啲內容....<br />\n好 撚 奇 怪 喎 Ching<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>POST 1</ins></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">有稅務大樓職員因早收趕得及替女兒洗腸<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/cRAyeS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/cRAyeS</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有早收工稅務大樓職員指，家中5歲女兒患罕見病，每日需要由她或丈夫「洗腸」。由於丈夫有事，她亦正值工作，因早收得以回家照顧女兒。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">早收職員李小姐說：「不停收到小朋友的短訊，因為他們在電視上看到一些片段，他們很擔心，幸好今天早收工，我作為一位母親可以陪在她身邊。不止是醫療需要，連心理需要，我都照顧得到。」</span><br />\n早收工稅務大樓職員黃小姐則指：「明白政府有不同陰謀、有不同手段，但我都有我的理智。所謂尊重，都要尊重市民有智力，不會受假新聞，或煽情故事影響。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>POST 2</ins></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">輿論戰已經開打，所有人都要幫拖<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/PfgHiU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/PfgHiU</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<br />\n大台新聞，有呢段：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有警員指，家中6歲女兒患罕見病，每日需要由她或丈夫「洗腸」。由於丈夫有事，本來由她負責，結果做不到。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">被困高級督察陳小姐說：「不停收到小朋友的短訊，因為他們在電視上看到一些片段，他們很擔心，但我作為一位母親甚麼都做不了。不止是醫療需要，連心理需要，我都照顧不到。」</span><br />\n被困警務處文職人員劉小姐則指：「明白大家有不同訴求、有不同需要，但我都有我的需要。所謂尊重，都要尊重不同人的需要。」<br />\n<br />\n兩個post既內容<br />\n紅色字對紅色字<br />\n藍色對藍色<br />\n<br />\n有冇人話我個<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">邊撚個先係真呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"cc1137b71d8a654f5a6d9f7807e04f869f571733","tid":1249444,"uid":198035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:19:37.000Z","msg":"警嫂果個係真 <br />\n<br />\nKen 嫂"},{"pid":"1f6c02a6232a25f1371e760194c5d582074ba923","tid":1249444,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:19:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e885e0f4219d5f1e1a080941d0045517aa966dd4","tid":1249444,"uid":107860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc1137b71d8a654f5a6d9f7807e04f869f571733","tid":1249444,"uid":198035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:19:37.000Z","msg":"警嫂果個係真 <br />\n<br />\nKen 嫂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:40:04.000Z","msg":"即係post1定2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef12cfe8aa0691f8247f98b923a9835e9c7f6d11","tid":1249444,"uid":44557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:25:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f231502943fd07af56fd6e5402cb6dd50e25bce6","tid":1249444,"uid":249971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:29:25.000Z","msg":"白色字都完全唔同"},{"pid":"390213c23a23a47ee8cdbaaddf80b68b84e2b9d1","tid":1249444,"uid":107860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f231502943fd07af56fd6e5402cb6dd50e25bce6","tid":1249444,"uid":249971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:29:25.000Z","msg":"白色字都完全唔同"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T09:21:22.000Z","msg":"我當住佢係兩個唔同人講既野唔理住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但紅藍字真係好離譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完全相反喎<br />\n<br />\n大台講到警渣好慘咁 <br />\n但實際邊個先係個洗腸妹妹老母？ 我又真係想知呀<br />\n直接扭曲事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇尋日訪問的士司機條片都睇到大台幾撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"> 所 以 我 唔 撚 會 信 大 台 講 野 架 屌 </span>"}]}